addCookieHeaders() - Method in class com.constantcontact.util.http.HttpsAuthProcessor
Add cookie headers to the current instance of AuthenticationConnection depending on the domain name.
Cookies are extracted from the Cookie Store found in the local Cookie Manager.
Cookies will be stored in a single header entry, and separated by ; just as HTTP protocol requires.
Handles both : perfect domain match (such as oauth2.constantcontact.com); partial domain match (such as .constantcontact.com);

TrackingBase - Class in com.constantcontact.components.common.tracking
Base class for all the Email Campaign Tracking classes used by the Email Campaign Tracking Service in Constant Contact.
Base class for all the Contact Tracking classes used by the Contact Tracking Service in Constant Contact.
It defines the common fields: Contact Id Activity Type Campaign Id Email Address Each sub-class will come with a particular value for Activity Type, depending on the answer type.
Each sub-class will also add its own new fields, depending on the business logic.
